uk.ac.uea.framework

Class FrameworkCopyright

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.uea.framework.FrameworkCopyright

  • public abstract class FrameworkCopyright
extends java.lang.Object
    An abstract class designed to provide a generic copyright class that displays the message of the University. When extended, this class allows the user to add their own name to the copyright message to create a full copyright message including both the creator(s) and the UEA. Created by Jack L. Clements
